# #Required Scopes Explanation

# ## `read_script_tags` & `write_script_tags`
# This scope is required to automatically inject our product customizer JavaScript (https://shopify.krcustomizer.com/scripts/config.v1.js) into the store's product pages. This enables the customization functionality to appear and work properly on your customers' product pages.

# ## `read_orders`
# Required to access order information for processing and fulfillment.

# ## `write_draft_orders`
# Necessary for creating custom pricing calculations and managing custom line items based on customer product customizations.

# ## `read_products` & `write_products`
# Required to access and modify product data, including displaying product information in the customizer and saving customization options.



